name: Line
description: Prime example of some BS contemporary art. It's a drawing of a line. Here at BS Contemporary Art Inc., we don't beat around the bush. It's pure, unadulterated BS.

name: Color Squiggles
description: Prime example of some BS contemporary art. Notice the infusion of colors as they mesh to mimic the diverse nature of the urban landscape. Or, observe the utilization of negative space as it contrasts the vibrant lines and seemingly formless shapes. Or just take it for what it is and stop making unnecessarily deep inferences as to what the piece means. Here at BS Contemporary Art Inc., we don't beat around the bush. It's pure, unadulterated BS.
